# User Journey: View Occupancy Analytics Dashboard

---

## Persona
- Office Manager

## Journey Goal
- Get a high-level overview of office utilization.

## Trigger
- Office Manager checks weekly occupancy trends.

## Steps

1. Log into the web app.
2. Access the "Analytics Dashboard" from the main menu.
3. View live occupancy rates.
4. Filter data by day, week, month, or custom period.
5. Identify underutilized areas.
6. Download detailed reports (optional).

## Success Outcome
- Understand space usage trends for planning decisions.

## Pain Points (to avoid)
- Overwhelming data visualization.
- Slow dashboard loading.

## Notes
- Include clear graphs (bar, line, heatmap) and KPIs at a glance.
